.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, grapes, peach, raspberry
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, manager, nurse, teacher
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, black, light-blue, green
4 different games are played: snooker, billiard, canasta, bridge
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hedgehog, lizard, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, ice-hockey, skateboarding, swimming
 1. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is swimming and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 3. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 8. the teacher is the person eating peach##1
 9. the person eating grapes is between the person playing canasta and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
10. the chef is on the left of the nurse##1
11. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
13. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
14. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
15. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
16. the person who likes green is the person playing snooker##1
17. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the chef##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea           | lemonade   | fanta      | milk     |
| Food          | peach         | grapes     | raspberry  | eggplant |
| Job           | teacher       | manager    | chef       | nurse    |
| Color   | green      | light-blue   | fuchsia  | black   |
| Game   | snooker      | billiard     | canasta    | bridge  |
| Pet           | hedgehog      | lizard     | guinea-pig | snake    |
| Sport         | skateboarding | ice-hockey | swimming   | biathlon |

