 8. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
10. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
